<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="W" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Weed1" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Weed,</orth> subst. garment: <cit><quote>the deed that spots and stains love's modest snow-white w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. luc 196" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 196</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>thy youth's proud livery . . . will be a tattered w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. son 2.4" default="NO" valid="yes">Sonn. 2, 4</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>keep invention in a noted w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. wiv 1.76.6" default="NO" valid="yes">76, 6</bibl></cit> (not to dress it new). <cit><quote>w. wide enough to wrap a fairy in,</quote> <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.1.256" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 1, 256</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>he wore the humble w.</quote> <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.229" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 229</bibl></cit>. <cit><quote>I will rob Tellus of her w., to strew thy green with flowers,</quote> <bibl n="shak. per 4.1.14" default="NO" valid="yes">Per. IV, 1, 14</bibl></cit>. Plur. <cit><quote>--s:</quote> <bibl n="shak. tgv 2.7.42" default="NO" valid="yes">Gent. II, 7, 42</bibl></cit>. <bibl n="shak. ado 5.3.30" default="NO" valid="yes">Ado V, 3, 30</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 5.2.811" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL V, 2, 811</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mnd 2.2.71" default="NO" valid="yes">Mids. II, 2, 71</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.262" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 262</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tn 5.262" default="NO" valid="yes">Tw. V, 262</bibl> <bibl n="shak. wt 4.4.1" default="NO" valid="yes">Wint. IV, 4, 1</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 3.3.229" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C III, 3, 229</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 4.1.104" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 1, 104</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tro 3.3.239" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. III, 3, 239</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cor 2.3.161" default="NO" valid="yes">Cor. II, 3, 161</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 1.70" default="NO" valid="yes">Tit. I, 70</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 2.1.18" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 1, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 3.1.43" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 1, 43</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. tit 5.3.196" default="NO" valid="yes">V, 3, 196</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. rom 5.1.39" default="NO" valid="yes">Rom. V, 1, 39</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. ham 4.7.81" default="NO" valid="yes">Hml. IV, 7, 81</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lr 4.7.7" default="NO" valid="yes">Lr. IV, 7, 7</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 5.1.23" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. V, 1, 23</bibl>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>